      when "7-2-2-B-b-iii-2"
        | adjectives, e.g., #[i Dúirt na gasúir go mb&rsquo;aoibhinn leo an cáca milis] #[+tl The children said that they loved the sweet cake];
      when "7-2-2-B-b-iii-3"
        | the demonstrative pronominals #[i eo], #[i in] and #[i úd], e.g., #[i Dúirt sé go mb&rsquo;in a raibh aige];
      when "7-2-2-B-b-iii-4"
        | adjectival adverbs, e.g., #[i Dúirt sé go mb&rsquo;annamh a théadh sé ann] #[+tl He said that he rarely went there].
